query:
SELECT ot.id, ot.templateId, ot.assignedAt, tt.uniqueId, tt.title 
FROM organizationTemplates ot 
LEFT JOIN taskTemplates tt ON ot.templateId = tt.id 
WHERE ot.organizationId = 330025
ORDER BY ot.assignedAt DESC;
